    "9585dbdf-5519-43bd-a4c5-6aa99afe9a31": {
      "type": "seo-content",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "",
        "heading_size": "h3",
        "text": "<p>At Grasse, we believe that self-care is an art form—a timeless expression of individuality and refinement. Our range of premium men's care products is meticulously crafted to elevate your daily grooming routine to an experience of indulgence and luxury.</p><p>Nestled in the heart of tradition and innovation, Grasse draws inspiration from the picturesque landscapes of the French Riviera. Named after the legendary perfume capital of the world, our brand embodies the essence of timeless elegance and uncompromising quality.</p><p>From nourishing face creams to invigorating body washes, Grasse offers a comprehensive collection of grooming essentials tailored to the modern gentleman. Whether you're refining your complexion or enhancing your natural allure, our products are designed to deliver unparalleled results, leaving you feeling confident and empowered.</p>",
        "content_alignment": "center",
        "section_width": "max-w-narrower",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "spacing_top": "2",
        "spacing_bottom": "2"
      }
    },
