    "seo_content_Xj8ngr": {
      "type": "seo-content",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "",
        "heading_size": "h3",
        "text": "<p>Unleash your inner debonair with our signature line of beard<br/>care essentials. Crafted with precision and expertise, our beard oils and balms are formulated to tame, nourish, and style your facial hair, ensuring a groomed and polished appearance that commands attention.</p><p>Indulge your senses with our exquisite range of candles and<br/>perfumes, each one a harmonious blend of sophistication and allure. From the warm embrace of aromatic woods to the refreshing zest of citrus notes, our fragrances captivate the senses and evoke a sense of timeless allure.</p><p>At Grasse, we are committed to redefining the standards of<br/>men's grooming, blending tradition with innovation to create products that transcend the ordinary and embody the extraordinary. Join us on a journey of self-discovery and refinement, where every grooming ritual becomes a celebration of your unique style and identity.</p><p>Elevate your grooming experience with Grasse—where sophistication meets masculinity, and indulgence knows no bounds.</p>",
        "content_alignment": "center",
        "section_width": "max-w-narrower",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "spacing_top": "2",
        "spacing_bottom": "2"
      }
    },
