        "tile_mGNxK8": {
          "type": "tile",
          "settings": {
            "show_on": "both",
            "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
            "custom_background_color": "",
            "heading": "Meet the founders",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "text": "<p>Grasse is the brainchild of a dynamic father-son duo, whose shared passion for quality and sophistication has redefined men's cosmetics. Drawing inspiration from the rich heritage of the world-renowned perfume capital of the same name, our founders have meticulously crafted a brand that embodies elegance, tradition, and modernity.</p><p>With decades of experience in the beauty and wellness industry, the father brings a wealth of knowledge and a discerning eye for quality to Grasse. His deep understanding of ingredients and formulations ensures that every product meets the highest standards.</p><p>The son, an innovator at heart, infuses the brand with a fresh, contemporary perspective. His commitment to sustainability and cutting-edge technology drives Grasse to constantly evolve, meeting the needs of today’s discerning gentleman.</p><p>Together, they have created a line of products that not only pamper the skin but also elevate the daily grooming ritual into a moment of pure indulgence. At Grasse, tradition meets innovation, delivering exceptional skincare solutions for the modern man.</p><p>Experience the refined luxury and meticulous craftsmanship of Grasse – where every product tells a story of passion, heritage, and a commitment to excellence.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "button--filled",
            "product": "",
